{
  "stem": "24195.3",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It was very dangerous, very hard labor for me.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I had to travel through on a bicycle.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "There was no public transportation.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I had to be there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I mean, not showing up there would have meant a lot of-- a lot of serious problems.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So I was in the wintertime all bundled up, half frozen, half-- complete almost totally stiff.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Take me half an hour before I thaw off in the-- in the locker room, change to the work clothes, you know.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And doing this, it was dangerous work because I almost get killed.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I'm not familiar.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I worked with among regular laborers.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "These will mostly older men, because all the young men were in the German army.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And they were not-- they didn't even know who I was.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "They probably wondered why I was there because young.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And I told them that I was not-- I had not been physically acceptable-- that's what I used-- for the German army.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "I wasn't going to say or tell them the real story.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "So they accepted that.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And they were actually nice to me.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "In fact, one of them practically saved my life when one of those big rollers was-- they weighed like three, four tons, and they were on these overhead cranes that they were moving across the aisles.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And I was in the way, and I didn't even notice it.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "I'm not-- I'm not familiar with factory work and this type of work.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "So at the last second, this thing would have crushed me if this roller, as it was going by.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "He pulled me into, into a corner, you know, out of the way.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And so after that, I thought I can't do this work.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And this is not fair that they're doing this.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
